# blog-priv#59: Consulting -> Hire Hoi URL migration. The old /consulting/* tree
# now lives at /hire-hoi/ai-consultancy/*. Explicit 301 (permanent) so search
# engines and externally cached share-cards follow the move.
# The bare /consulting (no trailing slash) needs its own rule: the wildcard below
# does not match a slash-less path, and there is no custom 404 to catch it.
/consulting /hire-hoi/ai-consultancy/ 301
/consulting/* /hire-hoi/ai-consultancy/:splat 301
